courseName: Advanced Clinical Practice (Advanced Neonatal Nurse Practitioner) MSc
facultyName: Faculty of Environmental and Life Sciences
description: Enhance your practice at a global top 100* university.This programme is designed around the needs of experienced neonatal practitioners looking to further develop practice and/or prepare for clinical practice roles at a senior level.You'll strengthen your existing knowledge, skills and competencies while also preparing for roles that require greater autonomy, responsibility and more complex clinical decision-making. You'll graduate primed to take the next step in your career.
fees: FeesPlease see the university website for further information on fees for this course.
